
Most people think of sex when they think of Scorpio, so one might think seducing one should be easy - wrong. Keep in mind that first of all, sex is not what a Scorpio is all about and secondly, they're too guarded to just give themselves to anyone. To seduce one, you have to be special enough. You have to appeal to their passion and be willing to show intensity, like them. Scorpio likes mystery, someone who keeps them guessing. They also appreciate confidence, show them you;re secure with yourself. Keep it real with them and be patient with their strong emotions.